spoilersthing

–block


It's alluded to in the interviews that the reason the -1's go to garbage is due to the feelings of insignificance or inferiority from their lives linger, and the town is the driving force in their reanimation. They feel they don't deserve proper burials, and thus, bury themselves in garbage. Regarding the origin of the anomaly, I chose to keep it ambiguous because I feel explaining everything about the town would take away from the mystery of the town and SCP.










